\pard\f0\fs28   ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b salonitana}: Leaves scabrid; segments lanceolate to oblong, entire or dentate. Involucre 15-20 mm in diameter; appendages acute or obtuse; fimbriae c. 1 mm. {\i Throughout the range of the species}.
